OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted grades unfit for    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpurpose, says ex-inspector 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A school leader who quit as an Ofsted  
OL,6, inspector after the death of Ruth Perry
OL,7, has told the BBC he felt his role could
OL,8, cause "more harm than good".           
OL,10,FHead teacher Ms Perry took her own life
OL,11,Fahead of a report that downgraded her  
OL,12,F"outstanding" school to "inadequate".  
OL,14,FTeachers in the National Education     
OL,15,FUnion (NEU) are being urged to refrain 
OL,16,Ffrom carrying out inspections for      
OL,17,FEngland's schools regulator.           
OL,19,FOfsted said most school leaders found  
OL,20,Fthem "constructive and collaborative". 
